# Part 5 – Vitamin D Classification (15 minutes)

Let's classify Vitamin D.

For learning, use:

| Vitamin D          | Status       |
| ------------------ | ------------ |
| Less than 20       | Deficient    |
| 20 to less than 30 | Insufficient |
| 30 or higher       | Normal       |

Write:

```python
